{"tid":2153116,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"★David Webb：買入282 不是支持公司，而是支持沽出股票的賣家。","createTime":"2020-08-12T10:51:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-12T10:54:14.000Z","uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"cd21095b47820578c0eafad87a802c48c450ac76","tid":2153116,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T10:51:31.000Z","msg":"有消息人士指，過去兩日證監會及聯交所就壹傳媒不尋常股價及成交量變動向個別證券業界查詢，並索取客戶資料、交易紀錄等。消息人士坦言，監管機構行動迅速，雖然他們向來有就股份異動進行查詢，在證券界內亦非「新鮮事」，惟過往通常事後才進行。東網已就此事向聯交所及證監會查詢，正待回覆。<br />\n<br />\n曾為壹傳媒主要股東的獨立股評人David Webb表示，<span class=\"xx-large\">投資者於市場上買入壹傳媒股票應要小心，因為這不是支持公司，而是支持沽出股票的賣家。</span><br />\n<br />\n證監會在周二發表聲明指出，收到大量詢問及注意到壹傳媒股價及成交額近期大幅急升。就此異常上升，強烈建議投資者謹慎行事，當局一直在監察、並將繼續密切監察交易情況，會要求壹傳媒盡快將所有信息向市場作出披露。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20200812/bkn-20200812095907180-0812_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20200812%2Fbkn-20200812095907180-0812_00842_001.html&d=bHO956KQIgsLkYPN5Vvl7U63eTsi4ka8iUmrXsVTuNg%3D&h=cda0c1ab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20200812/bkn-20200812095907180-0812_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"9da65b4856374ae3a9fc529dc64550c381d6521c","tid":2153116,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T10:51:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b0f8ec3a7f7aae65bb514d202d0db2ddf632d2f","tid":2153116,"uid":168930,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T10:52:46.000Z","msg":"老老實實<br />\n大股東都係佢地集團<br />\n只係將錢直接轉移姐<br />\nok嘅"},{"pi